description: I´ve met many nice boys during the last months. But I´ve never met an Adonis. Until today. But let me start from the beginning. Today´s interview was again for the position of a bartender. The first applicant today was almost not worth to be mentioned. Not my type. But the second one... Many of my friends told me that the boys from Slovakia are even more handsome than Czech boys. That was hard to believe - until today. He dint really have experience as a bartender before. In fact he worked as a salesman in a Boutique before. He was blond and his slim-fit shirt suggested that he was very well-built. He was more worried about the camera than about stripping naked to get the job. I assured him that the recording is only for my private pleasure...
title: Dirty Scout 29
